{"tid":1778451,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"張曉明，話叫香港要立即立23條","createTime":"2019-12-11T03:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T13:09:11.000Z","uid":156652,"like":9,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcedf2dd7a8d35aeba614fef7efda0871e0507b","tid":1778451,"uid":156652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"中國國務院港澳辦主任張曉明在《人民日報》撰文，指香港尚未完成基本法第二十三條立法，也未設立相應執行機構，是近幾年來港獨等本土激進分離勢力的活動不斷加劇的主要原因之一。 張曉明指建立健全維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制，強化執法力量，已經成為擺在香港政府和社會各界人士面前的突出問題和緊迫任務。張曉明又列出北京對特區的十項主權力，包括基本法修改和解釋權、對特區高度自治的監督權、向行政長官的指令權，以及北京根據需要向特區作出新的授權等，這些都需要加以制度化、規範化和程序化。 <br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/article/12-11-2019/58213\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F12-11-2019%2F58213&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwnO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=31b86536\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/article/12-11-2019/58213</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2019"},{"pid":"138ef0e231fcd25a2faf8dddd61e5ae6b3f987ac","tid":1778451,"uid":20870,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"三百萬不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48977e328a70eb1ab72fd130d27d895a0ce7cab7","tid":1778451,"uid":70527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:30:32.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"152322d278dbce70e629e2dd0b90c264d07e0e23","tid":1778451,"uid":133565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d1a4d1ee61634498110156f2caf9fd7d68d097","tid":1778451,"uid":331973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:31:00.000Z","msg":"快d立，要攬炒"},{"pid":"dd971cd47a8b09695aa39251c3f4931db578a248","tid":1778451,"uid":5627,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T03:31:04.000Z","msg":"條友想香港有真暴動"},{"pid":"9d41a3d8d7c81192dc458